	* src/protocol/http/auth.c:

	Some issues with NULL values of user and pass were fixed.  

Sat Nov 23 19:31:51 2002  Laurent Monin <zas@norz.org>:

	* src/protocol/url.c:

	Calls to memacpy(x, l) when x is NULL were removed.  

